QUANTUM TECHNOLOGY MANAGEMENT, LTD. V. APPLE COMPUTER, INC.

PLAINTIFF FILED THIS ACTION ON DECEMBER 21, 2005 IN THE UNITED STATES DISTRICT COURT FOR THE DISTRICT OF MARYLAND AGAINST THE COMPANY AND FINGERWORKS, LTD., ALLEGING

